; Enter filtered (disallowed) IP addresses in this file
; Wildcard characters (*, ^, ~) are allowed and ! negates the match
; IPv4 CIDR notation (e.g. 192.168.1.0/30) is also supported
; One IP/CIDR/wildcard per line. Matches here are BLOCKED BUT NOT
; LOGGED -- useful for known noise you don't want cluttering logs.
